From 5c84ba7b48632c6880aee9f4d09f9666dc458d38 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 3 Mar 2026 19:55:32 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] chore: remove duplicate and dead code files

- Remove src/main.ts, src/counter.ts, src/style.css, src/typescript.svg (Vite boilerplate leftovers)
- Remove src/components/layout/AdminLayout.tsx (unused duplicate; components/admin/AdminLayout.tsx is canonical)
- Remove src/components/shop/ProductCard.tsx (duplicate; components/shared/ProductCard.tsx is canonical)
  - Fix ShopPage.tsx to import from shared/ProductCard
- Remove legacy root-level pages (LoginPage, SignupPage, AccountPage, OrderDetailPage)
  - Real ones live in pages/auth/ and pages/account/ and are routed correctly in App.tsx
- Remove unused admin *Page.tsx variants (AdminDashboardPage, AdminProductsPage, etc.)
  - These had broken imports (formatINR from supabase) and were never registered in App.tsx routing
